title: Set up New pixel? When I dont have a pixel anymore?
content: I have issues with google emailing me about setting up my new Pixel, I used to have a pixel phone 3xl but have gotten a different phone different service and just set up a brand new gmail account for my acer spinbook 311.   and I got the pixel setting up email again?  is it because I set up a google account on my phone way back when and any google account associated with my number thinks I still have a pixel?  or is there a problem with my information being compromised.
